   Credit Ratings:
   Moody's Lowers
   Ratings on Debt
   Of Gulf Canada
   ----
   By Gary Lamphier
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
04/13/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C15
